  "description": "The time is a future where humans have moved their residence to the moon.... In the lunar colony, a game has become very popular. The name of the game is \"Run for the Money.\" It is an entertainment survival game in which fugitives are released into a limited area, and if they can escape from the pursuing android \"hunters\" until the time limit counts down to zero, they can win a large prize. Some dream of getting rich, while others challenge themselves to test their strength in \"Run for the Money.\" <br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)",
